<div class="container">

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12">

      <h3>Solutions to the Smart Grid Case</h3>
      <% solutions = data.solutions_smartGrid  %>

      Case resources:
      <ul>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/georghinkel/ttc2017smartGrids">Description and case resources</a> (Github repository)</li>
        <li><a href="TTC_2017_paper_1.pdf">Case presentation</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/georghinkel/ttc2017smartGrids/issues">Discussion of solutions and open peer reviews</a> (Github issue tracker)</li>
        <li><a href="https://goo.gl/forms/dghk91JBSZjGKZv63">Evaluation form</a> (Google Forms)</li>
        <li><a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1YuTCBNqoxR9gEUFcWGwzleDU1pbZUZSI5guGPpJlsp0/edit?usp=sharing">Open Peer Reviews</a> (Google Docs)</li>
      </ul>

      <p>The following <%=solutions.size%> solutions were submitted:</p>

      <table class="table table-striped table-bordered table-hover">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <!-- <th>
              Presentation<br/>
            </th> -->
            <th>Tool</th>
            <th>Authors</th>
            <th>Artefacts</th>
            <th>Opponents</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <% solutions.each_with_index do |solution, index| %>
            <tr>
              <!-- <td>
              </td> -->
              <td><strong><%=solution.tool%></strong></td>
              <td><%=solution.authors%></td>
              <td>
                <a href="solutions/smartGrid/TTC_2017_paper_<%=solution.pdf%>.pdf">PDF Description</a> <br/>

                <% if solution.share.empty? %>
                  <strong>No SHARE demo</strong>
                <% else %>
                  <a href="<%=solution.share%>">SHARE Demo</a>
                <% end %>
                <br/>
                <% if solution.scm.empty? %>
                  <strong>No SCM</strong>
                <% else %>
                  <a href="<%=solution.scm%>">SCM</a>
                <% end %>
              </td>
              <td>
                <%=solution.opponents.map { |index| solutions[index].authors }.join("<br/>")%>
              </td>
            </tr>
          <% end %>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>
